<DocsLayout title="Downloads" description="Download ostk binary releases for macOS and Linux. GPG-signed. Verify before you run.">
  <p>Binary releases of ostk, GPG-signed. Install via script or download directly.</p>

  <h2>Install script</h2>
  <p>The fastest path. Detects your platform, downloads the correct binary, verifies the GPG signature, and places it in your <code>$PATH</code>.</p>
  <pre><code>curl -fsSL https://ostk.ai/install | sh</code></pre>
  <p>The script always fetches the latest release. You can <a href="https://ostk.ai/install">view the install script</a> before running it.</p>

